====================================================================
====================================================================
RELEASE GOAL
====================================================================

Atlas Version 1.0 is complete when a founder can submit an invention once
and Atlas autonomously coordinates every participating department from
idea through commercialization.

The founder should be able to:

✓ Create an invention

✓ Upload supporting documents

✓ Receive autonomous analysis

✓ Generate engineering specifications

✓ Maintain a persistent engineering model

✓ Generate a native CAD model

✓ Evaluate manufacturability

✓ Assess patent readiness

✓ Research market opportunities

✓ Evaluate pricing

✓ Prepare licensing materials

✓ Prepare investor materials

✓ Generate executive reports

✓ Monitor autonomous department activity

✓ Approve only legal, financial, or strategic decisions

without requiring engineering, patent, manufacturing, or business
expertise.

====================================================================
