====================================================================
RELEASE BLOCKERS
====================================================================

Current Critical Blockers

• Market Intelligence (AT-011) not yet implemented.

• Financial Intelligence (AT-012) not yet implemented.

• Investor Intelligence (AT-013) not yet implemented.

• Advanced Document Intelligence (AT-014) not yet implemented.

• Final Autonomous Company integration (AT-015) not yet implemented.

------------------------------------------------------------

Known Verification Boundaries

The following items remain manually unverified and should be completed
before Version 1.0 release:

• Authenticated founder browser walkthrough.

• Complete end-to-end invention lifecycle validation.

• Long-running asynchronous execution verification.

• Cross-department package consistency validation.

• CEO Command Center production validation.

These are validation tasks—not architectural blockers.

====================================================================
KNOWN ISSUES
====================================================================

Current Known Issues

• Release Master Plan required reconciliation after major architectural
  milestones.

• Minor Next.js metadata warnings remain during production build but do
  not prevent successful deployment.

• Manual founder validation has not yet exercised every autonomous
  workflow from Engineering through Patent Intelligence.

No architectural regressions are currently known.

